OL,3,CPoundland saved from collapse - but 68
OL,4,Cstores across the country will close
OL,6,FPoundland has avoided entering
OL,7,Fadministration after a restructuring
OL,8,Fplan was approved by a judge at the
OL,9,FHigh Court, just days before the
OL,10,Fcompany was due to run out of money.
OL,12,FBarristers for the retailer had told a
OL,13,Fhearing earlier on Tuesday it would be
OL,14,Fplaced into administration by Friday
OL,15,Fand was set to run out of money by
OL,16,FSunday 7 September if the plan was not
OL,17,Fapproved.
OL,19,FThe scheme will see up to #60 million
OL,20,Fof new funding injected to keep the
OL,21,Fretailer afloat, among other terms.
