OL,3,CPoundland saved from collapse - but 68
OL,4,Cstores across the country will close
OL,6,FIt comes after the discount retail
OL,7,Fchain said it planned to permanently
OL,8,Fclose 68 shops after being sold for
OL,9,Fonly #1 itself.
OL,11,FPoundland, which has 14,700 members of
OL,12,Fstaff and around 800 stores, was
OL,13,Ffounded in Burton-upon-Trent,
OL,14,FStaffordshire in 1990.
