OL,3,CPoundland saved from collapse - but 68
OL,4,Cstores across the country will close
OL,6,FPoundland said it would also close its
OL,7,Ffrozen and digital distribution site
OL,8,Fat Darton, South Yorkshire, later this
OL,9,Fyear and another warehouse at
OL,10,FSpringvale in Bilston, West Midlands,
OL,11,Fearly next year, impacting a further
OL,12,F350 jobs.
OL,14,FThe company also plans to stop online
OL,15,Fsales through its Poundland.co.uk
OL,16,Fwebsite next month, and to retire its
OL,17,FPerks app.
