OL,3,CPoundland saved from collapse - but 68
OL,4,Cstores across the country will close
OL,6,FThree stores closed before July this
OL,7,Fyear, and 37 have closed this month,
OL,8,Fincluding in Newcastle, Leicester and
OL,9,FPeterborough.
OL,11,FAnother 11 stores, including those in
OL,12,FBlackburn, Kettering and Taunton, are
OL,13,Fdue to close on Sunday, and a further
OL,14,Fstore, in Irvine, North Ayrshire,
OL,15,FScotland, will close on September 14.
OL,17,FIn written submissions for the hearing
OL,18,Fon Tuesday, Tom Smith KC, for
OL,19,FPoundland Limited, said that its
OL,20,F"profitability has sharply declined"
OL,21,Fin recent years.
