OL,3,CPoundland saved from collapse - but 68
OL,4,Cstores across the country will close
OL,6,FHe said: "The group was performing
OL,7,Fwell prior to and during the Covid-19
OL,8,Fpandemic.
OL,10,F"However, the business has struggled
OL,11,Fin the last two years in an
OL,12,Fincreasingly challenging UK retail
OL,13,Fenvironment.
OL,15,F"Its response to these challenges was
OL,16,Fto broaden its offering, including by
OL,17,Fadding chilled and frozen products and
OL,18,Fintroducing online sales.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
