OL,6,F"However, these changes increased
OL,7,Foperating costs, as did increases in
OL,8,Fthe UK national living wage and
OL,9,Femployer national insurance
OL,10,Fcontributions."
OL,12,FIn court, he said a "very significant
OL,13,Famount of new money" would be injected
OL,14,Finto the company through the plan.
OL,16,FThe scheme will also see Poundland
OL,17,Fgiven a #30m overdraft and dates for
OL,18,Fthe retailer to pay back loans pushed
OL,19,Fback to 2028. Some of its rents will
OL,20,Falso be reduced under the plan.
