OL,3,CPoundland saved from collapse - but 68
OL,4,Cstores across the country will close
OL,6,FThe restructure does not cover
OL,7,FPoundland's operations in the Republic
OL,8,Fof Ireland and the Isle of Man, where
OL,9,Fit trades as Dealz.
OL,11,FNo-one has appeared in court to oppose
OL,12,Fthe plan being approved.
OL,14,FBarry Williams, Poundland's managing
OL,15,Fdirector, said following the hearing
OL,16,Fthat the decision was "vitally
OL,17,Fimportant for Poundland, allowing us
OL,18,Fto stabilise the business, securing
OL,19,Fthe future of hundreds of stores and
OL,20,Fthousands of jobs".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
