OL,6,FHe said: "Despite the opportunity this
OL,7,Fruling provides, I'm extremely mindful
OL,8,Fof its consequences for our
OL,9,Fcolleagues, especially those leaving
OL,10,Fus as we streamline our store estate,
OL,11,Fdistribution network and support
OL,12,Fteams".
OL,14,F"Nevertheless, our wider attention
OL,15,Fmust now turn to getting Poundland
OL,16,Fback to growth.
